front.title: Alert My Star Destroyer!
front.gametext: If your admiral, moff or Dark Jedi just shuttled aboard your Star Destroyer, deploy on that character. Star Destroyer is immune to attrition and Flagship deploys free on that starship. Immediate Effect lost if character not aboard that starship.
front.lore: For important Imperial dignitaries, an individual Star Destroyer is placed at their disposal.

combo: Alert My Star Destroyer! + Flagship Executor
